<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ToyMarket</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans+KR:400,700&display=swap&subset=korean" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/product.css">
    <script src="/public/js/common.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/product.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.0.js"></script>
</head>
<body onload="automatic_all()">
    <div id="up_menu">
        <span id="logo"><a href="/public/main.html"><img src="/public/img/logo.png"></a></span>
        <form action="/search/name" method="GET" id="search">
            <input type="text" name="search_word" id="search_word" required>
            <button id="search_button" type="submit">검색</button>
        </form>
        <span id="up_a_menu">
            <a href="/public/signup.html" id="signup">회원가입</a>
            <a href="/public/login.html" id="login">로그인</a>
            <a href="#" id="cart" onclick="cart()">장바구니</a>
            <a href='#' id='mypage' onclick="mypage()">마이페이지</a>
            <form action="/go_mypage" method="POST" name="go_mypage">
            </form>
        </span>
    </div>
    <br><br><br><br><br><br>
    <div id="list_menu">
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/search/id?Bid=0">게임</a>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/search/id?Bid=0&Sid=0">닌텐도 3DS</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/search/id?Bid=0&Sid=1">닌텐도 스위치</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/search/id?Bid=0&Sid=2">선불카드</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/search/id?Bid=0&Sid=3">아미보</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/search/id?Bid=0&Sid=4">기타</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><a href="#">퍼즐/블록</a>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#B1">레고</a></li>
                <li><a href="#B2">옥스포드</a></li>
                <li><a href="#B3">캐릭터 상품</a></li>
            </ul>
        </li>
            <li><a href="#">인형</a>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#C1">캐릭터 인형</a></li>
                <li><a href="#C2">봉제 인형</a></li>
                <li><a href="#C3">피규어</a></li>
                <li><a href="#C4">작동 인형</a></li>
                <li><a href="#C5">동물 인형</a></li>
            </ul>
        </li>
            <li><a href="#">야외/스포츠</a>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#D1">공</a></li>
                <li><a href="#D2">낚시/골프</a></li>
                <li><a href="#D3">비누방울</a></li>
                <li><a href="#D4">줄넘기</a></li>
            </ul>
        </li>
            <li><a href="#">조종/기차/자동차</a>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#E1">변신 장난감</a></li>
                <li><a href="#E2">조종 장난감</a></li>
                <li><a href="#E3">수집 장난감</a></li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="quick_menu">
        <span>퀵메뉴</span>
        <hr style= "border: 2px solid gray;">
        <span><a href="#" onclick="go_order_list()">주문 목록</a></span>
        <hr>
        <span><a href="#" id="cart" onclick="cart()">장바구니</a></span>
        <form action="/go_cart" method="POST" name="go_cart"></form>
        <hr>
        <span><a href='#' id='mypage' onclick="mypage()">마이페이지</a></span>
        <span><button onclick="Go_top()">TOP</button></span>
    </div>
    <div id="product">
        <img id="product_img" src="/public<%- result[0].image %>">
        <div id="product_info">
            <hr>
            <p id="product_name"><%- result[0].name %></p>
            <hr style="border: 2px solid black;">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>판매가</td>
                    <td id="price"><%- result[0].price %>원</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>할인가</td>
                    <td><span id="sale"><%- result[0].sale_price %></span>원</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>적립 적립금</td>
                    <td><span id="savings"><%- result[0].saving %></span>P</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>배송비</td>
                    <td><span id="shipping_fee"><%- result[0].shipping_fee %></span>원</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>제조국</td>
                    <td id="manufacturer"><%- result[0].manufacturer %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>상품 번호</td>
                    <td id="product_id"><%- result[0].id %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <hr style="border:1px solid gray;">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td><input type="number" step="1" value="1" id="product_count" required pattern="[0-9]+" title="주문할 상품의 갯수를 입력해주세요."  onkeyup="auto_cal()"></td>
                    <td><span id="total_price"><%- result[0].sale_price %></span>원</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <hr style="border:1px solid gray;">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td><button id="add_to_cart" onclick="add_to_cart()">장바구니</button></td>
                    <form action="/order/now" method="GET" name="order_now">
                        <input type="hidden" id="hidden_id" value="<%- result[0].id %>" name="id">
                        <input type="hidden" id="hidden_count" value="1" name="count">
                        <td><button id="buy_now" onclick="now_check()">바로 구매</button></td>
                    </form>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div id="related_product">
        <h1>관련 상품</h1>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <% for(var i = 0; i < 4; i++){ %>
                    <td><a href=/product?id=<%- related[i].id %>"><img src="/public/<%- related[i].image %>" id="related<% i+1 %>"></a></td>
                <% } %>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <% for(var i = 0; i < 4; i++){ %>
                    <td><a href="/product?id=<%- related[i].id %>" id="r1"><p id="related_title<% i+1 %>"><%- related[i].name %></p></a></td>
                <% } %>  
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    <br>
    <hr style="border: 3px solid gray;"><br>
    <div id="under">
        <div class="under_notice">
            <a href="#">회사소개 </a>|
            <a href="#">법적고지 </a>|
            <a href="#">회원약관 </a>|
            <a href="#">광고/임대문의 </a>|
            <a href="#" class="im">개인정보처리방침 </a>|
            <a href="#">윤리경영</a>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="info">
            <p>대표이사: ○○○</p>
            <p>사업자등록번호: ○○○-○○-○○○</p>
            <p>고객센터: 1234-5678</p>
            <p>사업장주소: ○○○○시 ○○구 ○○동 ○○건물 ○층</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>